<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />All who hate me whisper together against me;</para>

<para style="q1">against me they hope for my hurt.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />They say, "An evil disease holds on tightly to him;</para>

<para style="q1">now that he is lying down, he will rise up no more."</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />Indeed, even my own close friend, in whom I trusted,</para>

<para style="q1">who ate my bread,</para>

<para style="q1">has lifted up his heel against me.</para>
